    <briefdescription>
<para>\par \b Purpose\/ \:  To convert image documents (.bmp, .jpg, .tiff, .hdr, etc.) into the PNG format using PIL (Pillow) for standard images and OpenCV for exotic formats. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Converts image-like (.bmp, .jpg, .tiff, etc.) documents into PNG. Look to the :class:<computeroutput>~dedoc.converters.AbstractConverter</computeroutput> documentation to get the information about the methods&apos; parameters. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
